Picocalc_NESco License Overview

This repository is not under a single uniform license.

The current tree contains multiple components with different license sources:

- Project-owned top-level integration and most platform-side code:
  - MIT License
  - This includes the repository root LICENSE text below, and source files in
    `platform/` and `drivers/` whose headers say `MIT License`
- `infones/`:
  - GNU General Public License Version 2
  - See `infones/doc/GPL2`
- `fatfs/`:
  - FatFs license from ChaN
  - See `fatfs/LICENSE.txt`
- `font/`:
  - M+ / PixelMplus derived font data
  - See `font/LICENSE.txt`
- `core/`:
  - Source headers in the current tree say `MIT License`
  - Project status note: licensing / provenance for this subtree is not yet
    considered fully unified, so do not treat `core/` as a separately cleared
    standalone license block without reviewing the files in context

For convenience, the MIT text used for the project-owned part of the tree is
copied below.

